  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK574">
<l>uḷapōṉ mukattevaṉ ceyyu maḷaviṉāṟ </l>
<l> kaṇṇōṭṭa millāta kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Beyond appearing to be in the face, what good do they do, those eyes in which is no well-regulated kindness ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
